org.gearvrf.script

Class GVRScriptFile

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gearvrf.script.GVRScriptFile
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    GVRJavascriptScriptFile, GVRLuaScriptFile

    public abstract class GVRScriptFile
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents a script file, which can be attached to an object to handle events delivered to it.

    It can be used in two ways:

    • Use GVRScriptManager.loadScript(org.gearvrf.GVRAndroidResource, String) to load using a GVRAndroidResource object.
    • Construct the GVRScriptFile object and set the script text using setScriptText(String), or load it from a stream using load(InputStream).
